Class ContainsRemoveVisitor

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.cards.visitors.ContainsRemoveVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
ComponentVisitor
public class ContainsRemoveVisitor extends Object implements ComponentVisitor
Visitor used to remove cargo and batteries from BatteryComponent and StorageComponent.
